d 'CNCLEAN': module to standardize Chinese text in Stata
d
d   This command provides functions to normalize and standardize
d Chinese text strings in Stata, facilitating data cleaning and
d text analysis involving Chinese characters. 
d
d KW: data management
d KW: Chinese language
d
d Requires: Stata version 14
d
d Distribution-Date: 20250903
d
d Author:   Xiaokang Wu,  Nanjing University of Science and Technology
d Support: email   wuxk@@njust.edu.cn
d
f cnclean.ado
f cnclean.sthlp
